   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Restore schools for children in Peruvian Amazon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is aimed to improve and restore the infrastructure of two schools in poor conditions located in the riverside communities of Santa Rosa and Nuevo Israel, in the Peruvian rainforest. This task will be performed through the improvement and restoration of the school&apos;s infrastructure and the delivery of school supplies and furniture. With these actions, 114 students and 6 teachers will be benefited.</narrative>
  </description>
